<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<view>
  <tooltip>
    <target>inheritedCheckbox</target>
    <anchor>left</anchor>
    <html>Inherit monitoring</html>
  </tooltip>

  <tooltip>
    <target>monitorCheckbox</target> 
    <anchor>left</anchor>
    <html>Individually enable monitoring</html>
  </tooltip>

  <tooltip>
    <target>alertOnRestartCheckBox</target>
    <anchor>left</anchor>
    <html>Alert on restart</html>
  </tooltip>
    
  <tooltip>
    <target>eventSeverityCombo</target>
    <anchor>left</anchor>
    <html>Select event severity</html>
  </tooltip>

  <tooltip>
    <target>regexIncludeTextField</target>
    <anchor>left</anchor>
    <html>Matching processes will be selected.<br/>See: <a href="http://docs.python.org/2/library/re.html" target="_new">python regular expressions</a></html>
  </tooltip>

  <tooltip>
    <target>regexExcludeTextField</target>
    <anchor>left</anchor>
    <html>Matching processes will be excluded.<br/>See: <a href="http://docs.python.org/2/library/re.html" target="_new">python regular expressions</a></html>
  </tooltip>

  <tooltip>
    <target>regexReplaceTextField</target>
    <anchor>left</anchor>
    <html>Simplify the names of the matching processes. Also, combine multiple processes into one set, by giving them identical names.<br/>Example: <tt>.*--foo=(\w+)\b.*</tt><br/>See: <a href="http://docs.python.org/2/library/re.html" target="_new">python regular expressions</a></html>
  </tooltip>

  <tooltip>
    <target>replacementTextField</target>
    <anchor>left</anchor>
    <html>Replacement text.<br/>Example: <tt>my_process (foo: \1)</tt><br/>Backslash escapes are processed. Unknown escapes such as \j are left alone. Backreferences, such as \1 are replaced with the substring matched by capture group 1 in the replacement regular expression. The replacement will be applied wherever the replacement regular expression matches within the command line text.<br/>See: <a href="http://docs.python.org/2/library/re.html#re.sub" target="_new">python re.sub</a></html>
  </tooltip>

  <tooltip>
    <target>devicesbutton</target>
    <html>Display devices</html>
  </tooltip>

  <tooltip>
    <target>eventsbutton</target>
    <html>Display events</html>
  </tooltip>
  
  <tooltip>
    <target>saveButton</target>
    <html>Save</html>
    </tooltip>

  <tooltip>
    <target>cancelButton</target>
   <html>Cancel</html>
  </tooltip>

  
</view>
